title: EMIL KOZAK Beauty-contest
content:
To celebrate the 1 1/2 year anniversary of Emil Kozak - Barcelona designstudio, I am hereby inviting you to take part of the beauty-contest.  
The Winners will recieve Skatedecks, tees, fonts and badges.  
More info here: [www.emilkozak.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131014094907/http:/www.emilkozak.com/ "www.emilkozak.com")
